Smaller companies, scalable platforms, backable management teams

                In our â€œbuy-and-buildâ€ transactions we tend to invest in smaller companies that have scalable platforms and backable management teams in large, fragmented industries, where we believe there are substantial revenue and margin benefits from sector consolidation.
            














