Â“Common StockÂ”), of Hilton Grand Vacations Inc., a Delaware corporation (the Â“IssuerÂ”), and amends the initial statement on Schedule 13D filed on JanuaryÂ 13, 2017, and Amendment No.Â 1 to Schedule 13D filed
on MarchÂ 17, 2017 (collectively, the Â“Schedule 13DÂ”). Capitalized terms used but not defined in this Amendment No.Â 2 shall have the same meanings ascribed to them in the Schedule 13D. 
